WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Step 1: Share from iPhone.

2
00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:09.000
First launch: tap Allow to grant photo access.

3
00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Turn on your iPhone Personal Hotspot.

4
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Tap refresh to show the BeamDrop URL.

5
00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:53.000
Tap "Select Photos or Videos" and choose what to share.

6
00:00:54.000 --> 00:01:03.000
Step 2: On Windows, connect to your iPhone hotspot.

7
00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:08.000
Open a browser and enter the BeamDrop URL.

8
00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:30.000
Preview files, select items, or tap Download All.

9
00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:35.000
BeamDrop: iPhone to PC. No cables. No cloud.
